# ───────────────────────────── Unreal Engine ─────────────────────────────
# UE generates these; never commit them. Patterns are path-independent so they
# match wherever UE nests the project (e.g. unreal/AgeOfTheApes/...).
# Keep Config/, Content/, Source/, and the .uproject.
**/Binaries/
**/Build/
**/DerivedDataCache/
**/Intermediate/
**/Saved/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
*.VC.db
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.sln
*.suo
*.xcodeproj/
*.xcworkspace/
**/*.autosave

# ──────────────────────────── Asset working files ────────────────────────
# Blender backups and DCC temp files
*.blend1
*.blend2
*.tmp

# ─────────────────────────── Packaged/local builds ───────────────────────
# Packaged game builds are release artifacts, not source. Keep them outside git.
Builds/

# ─────────────────────────────── OS / editor ─────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
